<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>民间借贷 on 曹义德律师专栏</title><link>https://caoyide.com/tags/%E6%B0%91%E9%97%B4%E5%80%9F%E8%B4%B7/</link><description>Recent content in 民间借贷 on 曹义德律师专栏</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://caoyide.com/tags/%E6%B0%91%E9%97%B4%E5%80%9F%E8%B4%B7/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>借条怎么写才有效？少写一个字，钱可能就要不回来</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%80%9F%E6%9D%A1%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%86%99/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%80%9F%E6%9D%A1%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%86%99/</guid><description>借条和欠条一字之差，法律后果天差地别。借钱出去之前花三分钟看完这篇，省掉将来三年的麻烦。</description></item><item><title>别人欠你钱不还？不用打官司也能把钱要回来</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E4%BB%A4%E8%BF%BD%E5%80%BA/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 01:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E4%BB%A4%E8%BF%BD%E5%80%BA/</guid><description>欠钱不还，一定要打官司吗？律师告诉你一条更快的路——支付令。15天出结果，费用只要诉讼的十分之一。</description></item><item><title>朋友借钱你担保？一个签名，一套房子没了</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%8B%85%E4%BF%9D%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 00:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E6%8B%85%E4%BF%9D%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D/</guid><description>帮朋友在借条上签了个名，结果被执行了一套房子。担保这件事，99%的人都没当回事——等出事的时候，已经晚了。</description></item></channel></rss>